        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  .mms-section {\n    background: #f2ede8;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n  .mms-inner {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 48px;\n    align-items: center;\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .mms-images {\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    background: #ecd9cc;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .mms-images img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    object-fit: contain;\n    display: block;\n  }\n  .mms-content {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 24px;\n  }\n  .mms-heading {\n    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px);\n    color: #c9836a;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n  .mms-block {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n  .mms-block-title {\n    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.6vw, 16px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #222;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n  .mms-block-desc {\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.4vw, 15px);\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n  .mms-block-desc em {\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n  .mms-icons {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 32px;\n    align-items: center;\n    margin-top: 8px;\n  }\n  .mms-icon-item {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .mms-icon-circle {\n    width: 72px;\n    height: 72px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #ecd9cc;\n    border: 1.5px solid #c9836a;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .mms-icon-circle svg {\n    width: 34px;\n    height: 34px;\n  }\n  .mms-icon-label {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #333;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 700px) {\n    .mms-inner {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 32px;\n    }\n    .mms-icon-circle {\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 60px;\n    }\n    .mms-icon-circle svg {\n      width: 28px;\n      height: 28px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"mms-section\">\n  <div class=\"mms-inner\">\n\n    <div class=\"mms-images\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0742/4068/8311/files/Scalp_Scrub_Before_and_Afters.webp?v=1783361636\" alt=\"Before and After\" />\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mms-content\">\n      <h2 class=\"mms-heading\">Made for a Calmer,<br>Healthier Scalp</h2>\n\n      <div class=\"mms-block\">\n        <p class=\"mms-block-title\">Clears buildup without stripping your scalp.</p>\n        <p class=\"mms-block-desc\">Gentle exfoliating granules lift away flakes, product residue, and dead skin—never scratching or over-drying. Just a clean, breathable scalp ready to grow healthy hair.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mms-block\">\n        <p class=\"mms-block-title\">Soothes irritation—naturally.</p>\n        <p class=\"mms-block-desc\">Plant oils and calming extracts work as you massage, easing itchiness and redness for <em>your</em> specific scalp concerns. Say goodbye to harsh steroids, prescription creams, and constant flare-ups.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mms-icons\">\n        <div class=\"mms-icon-item\">\n          <div class=\"mms-icon-circle\">\n            <!-- Exfoliating granules -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n              <circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"18\" r=\"11\" stroke=\"#c47a50\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"14\" r=\"1.4\" fill=\"#c47a50\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"21\" cy=\"13\" r=\"1.1\" fill=\"#c47a50\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"13\" cy=\"20\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#c47a50\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"20\" r=\"1.6\" fill=\"#c47a50\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"23\" cy=\"17\" r=\"0.9\" fill=\"#c47a50\"/>\n            </svg>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"mms-icon-label\">Deep Exfoliation</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mms-icon-item\">\n          <div class=\"mms-icon-circle\">\n            <!-- Soothing leaf -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n              <path d=\"M12 24c-2.5-6.5 1.5-13 12.5-12.5-0.8 9.5-6.5 13-12.5 12.5z\" stroke=\"#c47a50\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n              <path d=\"M12.5 23.5L23.5 12.5\" stroke=\"#c47a50\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n            </svg>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"mms-icon-label\">Soothes Irritation</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
